# WebP Support Test

This document tests WebP image generation for charts and maps.

## Chart Test

```chart
{
  "type": "bar",
  "data": {
    "labels": ["Q1", "Q2", "Q3", "Q4"],
    "datasets": [{
      "label": "Sales 2024",
      "data": [120, 190, 150, 240],
      "backgroundColor": "rgba(75, 192, 192, 0.5)"
    }]
  },
  "options": {
    "responsive": true,
    "scales": {
      "y": {
        "beginAtZero": true
      }
    }
  }
}
```

## Map Test

```map
{
  "center": [40.7128, -74.0060],
  "zoom": 12,
  "markers": [
    {
      "position": [40.7128, -74.0060],
      "popup": "New York City"
    }
  ]
}
```

## Performance Comparison

This test allows comparing PNG vs WebP file sizes.
